OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine, dry and locally warm
OL,6,Fday for the bulk of the area with
OL,7,Fsunny spells building into the
OL,8,Fafternoon. However some early showers
OL,9,Fmay appear around the east coast.
OL,10,FLight winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry night with clear
OL,13,Fspells, though lower cloud building
OL,14,Fthrough the central Belt overnight.
OL,15,FWinds light and variable in direction.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
